    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >准备好化身为一名变身战士的<strong>制琴师</strong>。你能掌握吉他的力量，征服地下城，并成为终极吉他英雄吗？舞台已准备好，聚光灯属于你。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052870/extras/4b716739eadeed64e608baaca203b91b.webp?t=1764071472\" width=617 height=57 /></span>《制琴师》是一款动作类roguelike游戏，你将在其中深入地下城，与被诅咒的灵魂对抗，并收集资源。利用这些资源制作各种强力吉他，每把吉他都有独特的能力。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052870/extras/f53136d53dcfc5b136b24e5ed1084896.poster.avif?t=1764071472\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052870/extras/f53136d53dcfc5b136b24e5ed1084896.webm?t=1764071472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052870/extras/f53136d53dcfc5b136b24e5ed1084896.mp4?t=1764071472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052870/extras/25d8d13bd54ebe79f06b4281bd8b1915.webp?t=1764071472\" width=617 height=57 /></span>与被诅咒的灵魂战斗并收集材料，努力到达地下城的最终boss。在每个地下城中获得新的技能。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052870/extras/1cdaf1ea4577564150b5c7a5948c445e.poster.avif?t=1764071472\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052870/extras/1cdaf1ea4577564150b5c7a5948c445e.webm?t=1764071472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052870/extras/1cdaf1ea4577564150b5c7a5948c445e.mp4?t=1764071472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052870/extras/42702804bd71832d2986d37bab0488fc.webp?t=1764071472\" width=617 height=57 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052870/extras/d38b933145afb508bec5dda8f8cc3336.poster.avif?t=1764071472\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052870/extras/d38b933145afb508bec5dda8f8cc3336.webm?t=1764071472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052870/extras/d38b933145afb508bec5dda8f8cc3336.mp4?t=1764071472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052870/extras/9e7e1a3679f083a39965d6d56da39e77.poster.avif?t=1764071472\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052870/extras/9e7e1a3679f083a39965d6d56da39e77.webm?t=1764071472\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052870/extras/9e7e1a3679f083a39965d6d56da39e77.mp4?t=1764071472\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3052870/extras/16041858e6e9a577e8cb20006d8003a5.webp?t=1764071472\" width=617 height=57 /></span>作为一家吉他店的老板，你不仅要制作和销售吉他，还要升级你的店铺和角色。管理你的店铺，设置价格，并吸引顾客来赚钱。利用你的收入提升能力，使你成为终极吉他英雄。</p><p class=\"bb